concept.definition: MedlineCitation record reviewed at citation level (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
MedlineCitation record that is indexed without MeSH Headings (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
MedlineCitation record reviewed at journal issue level (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
MedlineCitation record not indexed for MEDLINE (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
MedlineCitation record that is a true MEDLINE record (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
MedlineCitation record that is indexed with original (older) MeSH Headings (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).

text.div:
This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/medline-citation-status defines the following codes:

Code Display Definition
Completed Completed MedlineCitation record completed (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
In-Process In-Process MedlineCitation record reviewed at citation level (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
PubMed-not-MEDLINE PubMed-not-MEDLINE MedlineCitation record that is indexed without MeSH Headings (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
In-Data-Review In-Data-Review MedlineCitation record reviewed at journal issue level (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
Publisher Publisher MedlineCitation record not indexed for MEDLINE (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
MEDLINE MEDLINE MedlineCitation record that is a true MEDLINE record (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
OLDMEDLINE OLDMEDLINE MedlineCitation record that is indexed with original (older) MeSH Headings (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#status_value).
